content: standujar: Drove a significant refactoring effort in `elizaos/eliza`, merging a large-scale change to move character builder logic to core (#6069, +3997/-2414 lines). They also resolved plugin documentation and scaffolding issues (#6071) and have an open feature PR to auto-inject plugins (#6068). This activity demonstrates a primary focus on refactoring, bugfixes, and feature work, with changes spanning code, tests, and documentation.
